          <ol>
              <h3>Welcome to the Ai-Arena Open Beta!</h3>
              <b>Open Beta?</b><br>
              The Open Beta is all about breaking things, finding Bugs and enhancing the Workflow.<br>
              Everyone is invited to upload a Bot to the Ladder :)<br>
              <br>
              <br>
              <b>Known Bugs and limitations:</b><br>
              Currently only Python Bots are supported. C++, DotNetCore, Java, Golang will be added soon. 
              <br>
              <br>
              <b>Instructions:</b><br>
              <li><a href="https://ai-arena.net/register">Register</a></li>
              <li>Read the <a href="https://ai-arena.net/rules">Rules</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://ai-arena.net/dl/MapPack.zip">Download</a> the Maps and the <a href="https://ai-arena.net/dl/python-example-bot.zip">Example Bot</a></li>
              <li>Create a Bot and train against basic Sc2-AI using the training Maps</li>
              <li>Upload your Bot to the Website and activate it</li>
              <br>
              Your Bot will be added to the Pool and starts fighting other Bots on the Ladder.
          </ol>
